Nadia Barentin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nadia_Barentin 0 Nadia Barentin (17 October 1936 – 22 March 2011) was a French actress, known for her theatre and film roles, including Les Blessures assassines in 2000.She was nominated for the Molière Award for Best Supporting Actress for Monsieur Klebs et Rosalie in 1993.
